Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.55,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了盖尔之后送你下地狱好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.75,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到杀人就受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:09.98,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把你们完全粉碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.43,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为古拉多斯星人的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:53.10,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,美国和苏联的火星基地 因为互射核弹而毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:57.40,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们因为无处可去在这红色的星球到处流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:01.94,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,而再度回到这无人观测基地来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:05.75,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为绝望而带来的疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:07.50,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然连唯一的伙伴也...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:10.66,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我 也是人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.29,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 敌人再度出现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:25.80,Layzner_Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}回应他的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:31.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,920)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}黑色凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.33,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,走第六号路线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:37.70,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要脱离目前的编队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.61,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,目标固定在28
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:45.93,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,三分钟后与敌人接触
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.88,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,进入战备状态 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:15.92,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:29.27,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,有三架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.57,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,他没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.14,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:37.27,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,身为最后藏身处的 这个无人观测基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.52,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 才休息一下 敌人就来来袭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:53.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1010)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}雷兹纳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.21,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,三架SPT极速接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:04.81,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,机种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.34,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,「无畏者」 所属为古雷斯科舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(480,980)}BRAVER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.08,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,DV15426
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.92,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,DV15427
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.00,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一架是「黑色凯撒」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.00,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(850,980)}GRIMEKAISAR
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.05,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,GK-10U-01
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.45,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,「黑色凯撒」？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.45,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(665,980)}GRIMEKAISAR
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.56,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,是前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:23.24,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:24.33,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:26.75,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是显示器架设的角度问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.05,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可以调整吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:34.40,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,总比什么都不做强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.28,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.96,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,英二 听得到吗 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:48.77,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给你最后的劝告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:51.93,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你接受我的劝降的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:55.13,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我将根据古拉多斯军特别军法反叛罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.45,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,在此将你处决
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:04:59.20,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:02.60,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,990)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}无畏者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.18,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再让你姐姐伤心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.37,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,那和我姐姐没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.44,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是她会伤心是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:10.73,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 越悲伤越好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.06,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔 你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.56,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要古拉多斯保证地球人的生命安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:18.65,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,并停止对地球的攻击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.82,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就投降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:22.72,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是古拉多斯星人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.01,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,地球人的事情和你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:27.68,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我体内流的血有一半是地球人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.37,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这些的时候 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:34.79,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我再说一句 投降吧 以古拉多斯人的身份接受制裁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.26,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不仅抢了SPT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:39.01,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,还杀了两名士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.07,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:43.23,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确是抢了SPT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.42,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可我没有杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:49.88,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,古斯特罗士官的两名部下 根据报告说是你杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.82,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说 他骗人的 盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.08,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他们的是古斯特罗他自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.97,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,是我亲眼看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:00.21,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这下不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:15.52,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你说的话是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:19.49,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我没说谎 我绝对没对那两人下手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:30.09,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.03,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:48.02,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:52.91,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:54.53,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:57.89,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你也想下地狱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:06:59.82,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了盖尔之后也送你下地狱好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:03.39,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到要杀人就忍受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.54,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你... 古斯特罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:14.11,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要向前辈射击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.41,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 快回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:20.93,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.98,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.67,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.36,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,侦测驾驶员的生命反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:38.05,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,有太空服保护 体温正常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:39.78,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说他没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:42.78,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.98,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 你的伤没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.54,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,向我射击的是古斯特罗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.23,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,古斯特罗 我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:58.44,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,要杀人灭口的 除了他没别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:02.14,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈！ 振作一点！ 前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:07.50,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,古斯特罗 我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.45,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈！ 盖尔前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:13.76,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈！ 你听到了吗！ 前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.11,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊！ 快一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.49,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 古斯特罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.53,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点啊 还不会操纵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.24,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 我又不是在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:34.07,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 你的伤 你的伤很重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:36.90,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 身体动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.85,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧 盖尔 看我收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:51.99,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼 不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:55.63,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在我就不能杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.34,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能坐视不理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.22,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的射击技术进步了 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.64,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,资质不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.14,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不是叛徒的话 应该会是个不错的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.39,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有的开关关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:31.36,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:07.24,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有能源反应 没有油渍反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.10,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,他把引擎关掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:11.58,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底躲在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.12,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,依然没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.08,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,一号镜头没有任何迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.44,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:48.38,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,分出胜负了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:51.23,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,是有干扰吗 也无法通信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.27,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,他说的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.86,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是那战斗兵器的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.03,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:06.00,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.16,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:14.19,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:16.47,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,锁定他 并放到主屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:23.82,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看 敌人瞄准了另一个敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:27.35,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,那驾驶员一定是就是他的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:28.82,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,快告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:29.46,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:33.65,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护他的前辈 他才战斗的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:37.54,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是安娜 我们刚才还被那驾驶员攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.78,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去 快回前辈那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:45.85,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:55.56,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,穿着太空服 没有异常 体温正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.09,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 给我看着 古斯特罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.24,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,发现SPT能源反应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.10,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:17.96,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼 我来当你对手 干的掉我的话就试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:32.21,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:47.71,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.37,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,有你这种人真是我们古拉多斯人之耻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.53,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈不是你的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:57.25,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你继续叫吧 我只想杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.25,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管什么敌人同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.32,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.23,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.29,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,转啊 再转啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:24.05,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,太勉强了 这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.02,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,比起敌人自由自在地移动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:29.81,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,他为了保护下面的驾驶员让自己行动受限
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:34.59,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,请解除现在的战斗命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.31,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,快从岩石区中脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.48,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能丢下前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:48.69,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,请解除命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:49.69,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.76,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我跑了的话 谁来救前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:53.69,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.65,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 如果你们听到的话 我拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:05.24,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都可以 请救救我的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:10.34,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在那SPT里的驾驶员 他很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:11.52,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,请救救他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.37,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈他受伤了 谁都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.92,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,趁我引开敌人时 请救救他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:20.18,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 竟拜托我们做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.94,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们 听到我的话请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:24.83,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,通话键 通话键
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:28.20,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 我们才不听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.51,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个驾驶员对你来说是前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.89,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,但他却是攻击我们联合国基地的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.36,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样 我还是希望你们能救救他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.32,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,导弹接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:48.00,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 只要给他药就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.16,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.97,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,对大家来说他可能是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:58.74,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可对我来说他是重要的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:06.32,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我去 给我治疗剂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:07.89,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:12.34,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我去 你们不要离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.70,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:14.85,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.58,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,给我药 我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:22.88,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,罗安 这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:31.25,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.38,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我一人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.96,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们 救救我的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:39.34,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,听到你的请求 大卫已经出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.83,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为那种东西能干掉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:08.24,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 你以为你是我的对手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:13.20,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:16.84,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,看到有东西出来 原来是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.53,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一招吧 地球的猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.74,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔 这次我一定干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:08.51,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟地球的猴子一起死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.36,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.09,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:33.57,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,看我不把你们打得粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:41.96,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准回路破损 命中率58%
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:44.66,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,古斯特罗 胜负已分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:48.69,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,能解除我杀人的罪名 只有现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.94,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:54.18,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:57.83,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要笑死人了 谁要投降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:59.00,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我下来了 古斯特罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.60,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:04.06,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,那我只好逼你下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:06.35,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣 那你就来试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.81,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你也拿我没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:11.48,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你无法下杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:14.36,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我超喜欢杀人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:18.57,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,危险信息 中弹率96.2%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:21.21,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有回避空间 敌人有先行攻击迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:22.40,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击目标停止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.58,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是驾驶舱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:25.88,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 那会杀了驾驶员的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.79,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就不会杀人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.60,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊 有种开枪看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.57,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,中弹率98%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:36.14,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,推测驾驶员生存率 0.2%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.73,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,英二 开枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:42.42,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,无法回避 请进行先行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.01,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢开枪吗 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.48,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,中弹率 98.4%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:50.68,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 像你这么没用的人 杀的了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:55.33,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,请进行先行攻击 中弹率99.3%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:56.85,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.53,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.46,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,已摧毁目标 危机解除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:02.00,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:08.98,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:09.99,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:17.08,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又托他的福 可以继续存活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:25.59,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我感觉到 他又背上了另一个沉重的十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:28.58,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,已根据正常程序摧毁敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:33.02,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我 开枪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:36.32,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,目标被击破 生命反应停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:40.98,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:44.19,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,生命反应停止 摧毁敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:48.49,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,生命反应停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:23:01.61,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,990)}那个人的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:06.39,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(729,990)}如果静静地凝视
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:13.75,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,990)}只要他在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:19.73,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,990)}就会觉得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.95,0:23:25.78,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,990)}比起任何的 甜言蜜语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:32.95,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715,990)}我最喜欢的还是此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:39.60,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(735,990)}只要五分钟就好 让我尽情地说出一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:45.25,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(750,990)}不要再想别的了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:50.50,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(713,990)}Don't say...Don't say...anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:57.12,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,要活下去的话不战斗不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:01.43,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是叛徒 还说什么不要杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.55,0:24:04.21,Default_Sub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要 我不想杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.24,0:24:08.40,Layzner_Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs150\c&HE5E8DC&\pos(720,770)}追求生存之道
